    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/7e6d7e5e1c88718de57884ddfd835602.webp?t=1752286364\" width=608 height=32 /></span>关于本作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Simulation Room</i>是一款结合卡牌构筑元素的高速2D自动战斗游戏，灵感来源于<i>MegaMan Battle Network</i>。每回合，你将释放强力程序组合——施展华丽攻击、提升能力、召唤盟友并掌握强大武器。改变天气与地形，巧用装置策略以智取敌人，掌控战场。每一步都可能扭转战局——你是统御模拟，还是被数据抹除？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/5ac9d9280c6e15948e6cf20e4a50be03.poster.avif?t=1752286364\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/5ac9d9280c6e15948e6cf20e4a50be03.webm?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/5ac9d9280c6e15948e6cf20e4a50be03.mp4?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集强力程序</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集多种强力程序以强化你的卡组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/ea9122c223769b9b07426af4978ff532.poster.avif?t=1752286364\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/ea9122c223769b9b07426af4978ff532.webm?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/ea9122c223769b9b07426af4978ff532.mp4?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造毁灭性连击</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同步程序以生成终极组合，或按策略顺序链式释放，瞬间击溃敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/ba1b58b8510f9ecae8fbe4c99791ff5a.poster.avif?t=1752286364\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/ba1b58b8510f9ecae8fbe4c99791ff5a.webm?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/ba1b58b8510f9ecae8fbe4c99791ff5a.mp4?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与多样敌人战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多种场景和环境下，与各式各样的敌人展开激烈对抗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/f6e071181c7764f56be9b57b40eace96.poster.avif?t=1752286364\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/f6e071181c7764f56be9b57b40eace96.webm?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/f6e071181c7764f56be9b57b40eace96.mp4?t=1752286364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297570/extras/83204efdd38fa2ff0b214e1accec05a7.webp?t=1752286364\" width=608 height=32 /></span></p>",
